{
  "stem": "5103.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They keep dogs up in the top, they have special dogs there for the-- because they have to keep an eye if anybody strange comes in the house.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So whenever this child used to start wanting to come up, the father-- Father Visser used to say, you know, the dogs are up there, you realize that?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father, his father, and my uncle used to start barking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Barking like proper dogs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and woo!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, you know, and the child used to run downstairs and really think that there were dogs locked up in that house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we lived in constant kind of fear, but then there was one day where there was-- that area was going to be taken for raid.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They decided that street and surrounding streets, Germans were coming in to check the houses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anybody hiding anybody, Jews and non-Jews, they wanted to check it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So my father said, we-- you know, we better do something here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What is happening?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Where can we hide?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And Father Visser said, I don't know, and they all started putting their head together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, they found in the toilet downstairs, there was only a square-- no bigger than where you actually have your toilet-- and a little surrounding with the wash basin.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they decided that they're going to-- usually under toilets there's sand, sand and where they have pipes running.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they decided they're going to cut a piece where the toilet is, wood out of the [? failings, ?] and they're going to make a lid, lift it, and then dig, dig, dig, dig, dig.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then under that house, we will go in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When there's a raid, we will all go in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
